OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FPatches of low cloud and any
OL,6,Ffog will soon clear to leave a dry day
OL,7,Facross the country. There will be some
OL,8,Fdecent spells of sunshine, and with
OL,9,Flight winds it will feel very warm
OL,10,Fagain in the afternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FIt will be a dry evening with
OL,13,Fclear periods. Cloud will gradually
OL,14,Fincrease from the north overnight,
OL,15,Fperhaps bringing the odd spot of
OL,16,Fdrizzle later. Staying quite warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
