OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FSome sunshine will develop
OL,6,Fon Saturday morning, though cloud is
OL,7,Fset to increase from the north later,
OL,8,Fwith some showery rain developing for
OL,9,Fthe afternoon. Still warm, though
OL,10,Frather breezy.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FSunday
OL,13,Fwill be a fresher, still breezy day
OL,14,Fwith sunshine and scattered showers.
OL,15,FSome sunshine at times early next week
OL,16,Ftoo, though patchy rain is possible,
OL,17,Fchiefly in the north.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
